reviews.text: A very local place that serves simple and tasty food. Just a place to sit n eat. Not for fussy clean ppl 😅
Loved this place. The food was very high quality. Looking forward to going back.

Local, affordable cart noodles place which serves noodles with Macau-inpsired ingredients. Their pork chop bun is a must-try too. The sauce was well balanced but the pork chop was a tad on the dry side. While for the cart noodles, I would recommend choosing the Portuguese sausage as topping which wasn't on the menu.
Authentic local cuisine. English menu available. Reasonably priced
Very bargain price but service could be better.  Place is quite untidy with overcrowded tables and stools.

reviews.text:
價錢偏貴,味道一般,野飲還好,豬排包己經唔好食
(回顧歷史)03年我係第一次食,好好食,往事只能回味
麻辣豬頸肉，正！價格經濟，食物質素好！
A very local place that serves simple and tasty food. Just a place to sit n eat. Not for fussy clean ppl 😅
澳門式車仔麵，沙茶醬汁非常正。辣蛋是辣味蛋餅，有驚喜。豬扒包塊豬扒較薄，醬汁味道酸甜適中。

中環價位尚可的店家
店內裝潢也很香港的感覺
奶茶還不錯 不會太苦(有小甜 走甜的選擇)
細麵比較硬 雞翅夠味 墨魚丸稍軟
